U(x,t) = \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} B_n e^{-n^2 \pi^2 \kappa t/a^2} \sin{\left ( \frac{n \pi x}{a}\right )}
U(x,0) = \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} B_n \sin{\left ( \frac{n \pi x}{a}\right )}
u
B_n
B_n = \frac{2}{a} \int_0^a dx \, \left ( -\frac{x}{a} \right ) \sin{\left ( \frac{n \pi x}{a}\right )} = -\frac{2}{a^2} \int_0^a dx \; x \sin{\left ( \frac{n \pi x}{a}\right )}
U(x,0)=-x/a
 \begin{gather} B_n=\frac{2}{a}\int\limits_0^a U(x,0)\sin{\biggl(\frac{n{\pi}x}{a}\biggr)}dx= -\frac{2}{a^2}\int\limits_0^a x\sin{\biggl(\frac{n{\pi}x}{a}\biggr)}dx=\\ =\frac{2}{an\pi}\int\limits_0^a x\,d\cos{\biggl(\frac{n{\pi}x}{a}\biggr)}= \frac{2}{an\pi}x\cos{\biggl(\frac{n{\pi}x}{a}\biggr)}\biggr|_0^a-\frac{2}{an\pi} \int\limits_0^a \cos{\biggl(\frac{n{\pi}x}{a}\biggr)}dx=\\ =\frac{2}{n\pi}\cos{(n\pi)}-\frac{2}{n^2{\pi}^2}\sin{\biggl(\frac{n{\pi}x}{a}\biggr)} \biggr|_0^a=\frac{2(-1)^n}{n\pi}. \end{gather} 
